PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Honourable Harvie Andre of the Honourable Stuart Douglas Boland Smith, Q.C., of Kamloops, British Columbia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Post Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of R.
